title: After BroodWar Campaigns - A Starcraft Odyssey.zip
description:
These campaigns are for the war-torn veterans of Brood War. Only they might appreciate the storyline, let alone stand a chance against the beast that "A Starcraft Odyssey" is. 

The story picks up after the events on "Omega". That could mean some months, or most probably a couple of years after the events of Brood War (there is no strict time-frame). 
The new campaigns find most of the characters from Brood War still alive and well, ready for a new circle of carnage!
